						<div class="postbody">I'm not sure if I understand what you want to do? Either you want to hack a game to move the text to the left.....or you want to scroll some text from left to right. 
<br />
<br />On nes theres no specific text "routines" or anything you'd have to draw your text as backround (you could do sprites but then you cant have more then 8 letters) and use the scroll register to scroll them. I suggest either just learning how to do a single sprite first or learn how to scroll the backround.</div>

