					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Working on a translation, perhaps?  We really need every last detail we can get, about what you're wanting to do, in order to help.
<br />
<br />Background tile data (text) is written to $2007, which auto-increments the address.  To draw it backwards (right to left), you will have to decrement the address manually, write that to $2006, for every byte you put out to $2007.</div>

