					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">You can do away with this whole draw right to left business. Say that I had this in a buffer:
<br />
<br />"Hello, world"
<br />
<br />And I wanted it to display as:
<br />
<br />"dlrow ,olleH"
<br />
<br />All I'd have to do is:
<br />
<br />ldy #11
<br />-
<br />lda Buffer,y
<br />sta $2007
<br />dey
<br />bne -
<br />
<br />Assuming PPU increment 1 is on. Also, if the buffer contains something like "dlrow ,olleH" you can draw it as is on the screen.</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

